divs: Sighting DetailsDark out, nighttime. Some kind of rectal linear aircraft slowly drifted over. There were lights on it, kind of looked like aircraft lights I guess. It was totally quiet. I was driving to the dump. Noticed it, stopped for a look. I watched it drift over me. Maybe 500-3000 ft. altitude. Pretty big, a big big aircraft if it was aircraft. I think it was some kind of airforce blimp??
